WEBVTT

00:21.184 --> 00:22.464
â™ªThat dayâ™ª

00:22.880 --> 00:24.448
â™ªNothing stays together foreverâ™ª

00:24.448 --> 00:25.792
â™ªI've quit romanceâ™ª

00:26.218 --> 00:27.920
â™ªWho hasn't failed againâ™ª

00:27.920 --> 00:31.424
â™ªCrying in deathâ™ª

00:31.424 --> 00:34.016
â™ªAnd in lifeâ™ª

00:34.432 --> 00:36.370
â™ªEven nowâ™ª

00:36.672 --> 00:38.656
â™ªWe keep learningâ™ª

00:38.656 --> 00:39.680
â™ªIt's no surpriseâ™ª

00:39.744 --> 00:42.144
â™ªBeing happy is so hardâ™ª

00:42.144 --> 00:43.968
â™ªWeirdly, I became a role modelâ™ª

00:44.736 --> 00:46.688
â™ªOn the day we met again, we said hiâ™ª

00:46.688 --> 00:52.896
â™ªIt was a reminder,
a test, and a complaintâ™ª

00:52.896 --> 00:56.003
â™ªWho can do anything without regretâ™ª

00:56.003 --> 00:59.424
â™ªI am all rightâ™ª

01:00.480 --> 01:05.074
â™ªMay you live in peaceâ™ª

01:05.074 --> 01:07.456
â™ªLet the world roarâ™ª

01:07.456 --> 01:09.732
â™ªSounds like a carnivalâ™ª

01:09.732 --> 01:14.453
â™ªBeing alive is never dullâ™ª

01:14.453 --> 01:18.830
â™ªHow wonderful to be freeâ™ª

01:18.830 --> 01:23.485
â™ªI became even better without youâ™ª

01:23.485 --> 01:25.824
â™ªNothing can be perfectâ™ª

01:25.824 --> 01:28.224
â™ªWe bless each other in painâ™ª

01:28.224 --> 01:34.234
â™ªWe nod and smileâ™ª

01:35.328 --> 01:36.288
â™ªMay we both be wellâ™ª

01:36.288 --> 01:41.024
= Love's Ambition=

01:41.040 --> 01:43.921
=Episode 30=

01:45.178 --> 01:45.698
Thank you.

01:48.098 --> 01:49.978
This is considered
a celebration banquet today.

01:50.417 --> 01:50.978
Of course.

01:51.937 --> 01:52.497
Lin Tao,

01:53.618 --> 01:55.538
do you know how I felt
when the bank notified me

01:55.618 --> 01:56.777
that the loan was disbursed

01:56.777 --> 01:57.937
into the company's account?

01:59.338 --> 02:00.458
I was overjoyed.

02:00.657 --> 02:01.898
That was special privilege.

02:01.937 --> 02:03.657
How did I get such an amazing friend?

02:04.217 --> 02:05.898
A thousand words come down to this.

02:06.538 --> 02:07.497
Thank you.

02:07.618 --> 02:09.298
Thank you for doing me such a big favor

02:09.537 --> 02:10.497
and helping Yan Studio.

02:17.178 --> 02:18.738
This is actually

02:19.578 --> 02:20.738
the first time we're dining

02:20.738 --> 02:22.257
in such a nice restaurant atmosphere

02:24.257 --> 02:25.418
and you're speaking to me

02:25.418 --> 02:26.418
so gently.

02:27.817 --> 02:28.697
For this moment,

02:28.697 --> 02:29.377
I feel

02:30.097 --> 02:31.377
every effort was worthwhile.

02:32.257 --> 02:33.937
Why are you talking so strangely today,

02:33.937 --> 02:34.458
Lin Tao?

02:36.298 --> 02:36.817
Am I?

02:37.898 --> 02:39.338
Stop overthinking, okay?

02:40.112 --> 02:41.418
What do you think I'm thinking?

02:41.777 --> 02:43.257
Then I'm overthinking.

02:43.657 --> 02:44.618
Anyway, now we are just

02:44.618 --> 02:45.657
good colleagues.

02:45.657 --> 02:46.578
Nothing more, right?

02:46.618 --> 02:47.458
Who says nothing?

02:51.418 --> 02:52.377
I worked tirelessly

02:54.298 --> 02:56.097
for you,

02:56.817 --> 02:58.138
creating that perfect

02:58.138 --> 02:59.738
financial report.

03:01.298 --> 03:03.018
I boosted Yan Studio's profits

03:03.138 --> 03:05.497
to 21 percent.

03:07.138 --> 03:08.697
That's what convinced the bank.

03:10.578 --> 03:11.618
Wh-What do you mean?

03:12.018 --> 03:14.298
With Yan Studio's current operations,

03:15.377 --> 03:16.497
we couldn't meet

03:16.497 --> 03:17.858
the bank's loan standards.

03:18.377 --> 03:20.298
It's all because they saw my report

03:20.298 --> 03:21.537
that we slipped through

03:22.298 --> 03:23.697
and the approval went smoothly.

03:29.338 --> 03:30.298
Lin Tao,

03:31.377 --> 03:33.898
this counts as fraud.

03:34.497 --> 03:35.858
This is loan fraud.

03:36.537 --> 03:37.497
Not me.

03:38.578 --> 03:39.618
It was your sister,

03:40.418 --> 03:41.977
Yan Studio's legal representative,

03:42.298 --> 03:43.738
Xu Yan.

03:45.537 --> 03:46.418
What are you implying?

03:47.618 --> 03:48.497
What do you want?

03:48.817 --> 03:50.338
What I want

03:50.338 --> 03:51.338
has never changed.

03:52.097 --> 03:53.298
Break up with Yu Yiming

03:54.018 --> 03:55.418
and marry me back home.

03:58.898 --> 03:59.657
Wait, Lin Tao.

04:03.097 --> 04:05.178
Didn't you let this go already?

04:05.338 --> 04:06.697
What? You were faking it?

04:08.138 --> 04:09.377
You've been acting all along?

04:11.298 --> 04:12.257
I can report you.

04:12.257 --> 04:13.738
I'll go report you right now.

04:13.738 --> 04:14.497
- I'm warning you.
- Go ahead.

04:15.338 --> 04:16.377
Go right now.

04:16.577 --> 04:18.817
I'm just an accountant.

04:19.658 --> 04:21.538
Without authorization
from the legal person,

04:21.538 --> 04:23.017
would I dare to cook the books?

04:24.257 --> 04:25.697
Why would I even need to do that?

04:26.017 --> 04:27.697
Every cent of the company

04:27.858 --> 04:29.457
didn't enter my pocket.

04:29.817 --> 04:30.457
Besides,

04:31.017 --> 04:32.137
the stamp on the report

04:32.137 --> 04:33.658
was applied by you, wasn't it?

04:35.298 --> 04:36.577
The company has surveillance.

04:37.298 --> 04:38.137
I checked it.

04:39.218 --> 04:40.738
Your stamping process

04:40.817 --> 04:42.298
is crystal clear.

04:43.618 --> 04:45.017
If you dare report me,

04:45.058 --> 04:46.897
I'll drag Xu Yan down with me.

04:48.738 --> 04:51.098
The legal representative
bears primary responsibility.

04:51.457 --> 04:53.858
Yan Studio is already crumbling

04:55.178 --> 04:56.858
under Shen Haoming's influence.

04:58.457 --> 05:00.618
Can you withstand
the bank's investigation?

05:02.577 --> 05:03.817
You're truly terrifying.

05:05.298 --> 05:06.218
We kindly took you in

05:06.218 --> 05:07.538
to work at the company,

05:07.697 --> 05:08.618
and you repay us

05:08.618 --> 05:09.218
with betrayal?

05:20.377 --> 05:21.697
Be realistic, Lin.

05:37.377 --> 05:39.137
Call me despicable

05:39.978 --> 05:41.058
or filthy,

05:42.298 --> 05:43.058
whatever you like.

05:47.866 --> 05:49.232
(Balance Sheet)

05:51.778 --> 05:52.577
But today,

05:52.577 --> 05:54.017
you must make a decision.

05:55.178 --> 05:56.178
Right now.

05:57.058 --> 05:57.778
Or else,

05:58.337 --> 05:59.418
it's mutual destruction.

06:03.618 --> 06:04.418
As long as you

06:06.098 --> 06:07.178
promise me

06:07.577 --> 06:08.897
that my sister

06:09.178 --> 06:10.298
and Yan Studio

06:10.298 --> 06:11.337
won't be troubled.

06:12.058 --> 06:14.032
(Balance Sheet)

06:15.298 --> 06:16.058
I'll do it.

06:25.298 --> 06:26.017
So,

06:27.778 --> 06:29.538
when will you break up with Yu Yiming?

06:33.377 --> 06:35.218
No need to rush this.

06:36.058 --> 06:37.457
Can't you give me some time?

06:37.978 --> 06:38.497
Fine.

06:39.658 --> 06:40.538
One week.

06:55.497 --> 06:56.658
Jinsong. Jinsong.

06:56.697 --> 06:57.858
Quick, call the doctor!

06:57.978 --> 06:58.618
Doctor!

06:58.817 --> 06:59.257
Doctor!

06:59.257 --> 06:59.738
Jinsong!

06:59.817 --> 07:00.337
Jinsong!

07:00.337 --> 07:01.058
Are you okay?

07:01.098 --> 07:01.697
Hurry!

07:03.137 --> 07:03.937
Jinsong!

07:04.418 --> 07:04.937
How is he?

07:05.137 --> 07:06.218
Family members out please.

07:06.218 --> 07:06.778
Calm down.

07:06.778 --> 07:07.697
Please wait outside.

07:07.778 --> 07:09.058
You'll hinder the resuscitation.

07:09.178 --> 07:10.298
- Jinsong.
- Please leave now.

07:10.457 --> 07:11.497
Prepare for CPR.

07:30.074 --> 07:31.152
(Haoming)

07:33.402 --> 07:35.248
(Haoming)

07:38.697 --> 07:39.257
Hui,

07:39.497 --> 07:40.778
please look after Haochen.

07:40.897 --> 07:41.978
Emergency at the hospital.

07:41.978 --> 07:42.538
Okay.

07:46.377 --> 07:46.858
Mom.

07:49.937 --> 07:50.538
You're here.

07:52.257 --> 07:53.178
How is he?

07:55.377 --> 07:57.257
His blood pressure
and pulse dropped earlier.

07:57.858 --> 07:58.858
It took a long time

07:58.858 --> 07:59.618
to bring him back.

08:01.418 --> 08:02.538
He just finished tests.

08:03.178 --> 08:04.978
All vitals are stable now.

08:07.257 --> 08:07.778
It's fine.

08:09.897 --> 08:10.858
How's Haochen?

08:14.978 --> 08:15.978
Same as before.

08:21.377 --> 08:22.978
Haochen can't have any more setbacks.

08:25.658 --> 08:26.658
Yan, I'm counting on you.

08:28.538 --> 08:29.017
Mom.

08:33.778 --> 08:34.977
If you keep pushing yourself,

08:34.977 --> 08:36.617
your health will collapse.

08:37.577 --> 08:38.337
How about this?

08:38.577 --> 08:39.937
You go rest and be with Haochen.

08:40.178 --> 08:40.857
I'll stay here.

08:41.217 --> 08:41.778
Okay?

08:43.298 --> 08:43.857
Alright.

08:45.337 --> 08:46.258
I'll stay a bit longer.

08:53.898 --> 08:54.977
Where's Haoming?

08:57.778 --> 08:58.778
He was here moments ago.

08:58.778 --> 09:00.337
Maybe he went to the nurses' station.

09:02.418 --> 09:03.337
I'll go look for him.

10:07.617 --> 10:08.378
I know.

10:13.617 --> 10:15.018
I know you're hurting.

10:27.298 --> 10:28.097
You know.

10:31.097 --> 10:31.937
Back in England,

10:31.937 --> 10:33.138
with everything that happened,

10:35.418 --> 10:37.178
if my parents hadn't shielded me,

10:39.857 --> 10:40.697
I couldn't

10:40.697 --> 10:41.857
have handled any of it.

10:43.258 --> 10:44.898
But after all these years,

10:44.977 --> 10:46.018
the consequences

10:46.018 --> 10:46.898
and responsibilities

10:46.977 --> 10:48.337
still fall on them.

10:53.658 --> 10:54.457
I understand.

10:57.857 --> 10:59.217
I fully understand

10:59.977 --> 11:00.737
how much Jinda

11:00.737 --> 11:02.178
and Haochen

11:02.977 --> 11:04.097
mean to my father.

11:08.217 --> 11:10.457
Both were nurtured personally

11:11.937 --> 11:13.498
by him from the ground up.

11:14.617 --> 11:15.857
That's why he suffered

11:15.857 --> 11:16.937
such a massive shock.

11:20.617 --> 11:21.298
I know.

11:22.937 --> 11:24.617
Your father greatly influenced you.

11:27.058 --> 11:27.817
You know.

11:32.138 --> 11:32.817
Since childhood,

11:32.817 --> 11:34.857
I've always seen him as a mountain.

11:39.617 --> 11:41.337
No matter the crisis

11:42.178 --> 11:43.178
or challenge,

11:44.418 --> 11:45.658
he could resolve anything.

11:47.538 --> 11:48.298
All these years,

11:48.337 --> 11:49.697
despite constant power struggles

11:50.977 --> 11:52.178
within the group,

11:53.138 --> 11:54.857
he balanced competing interests

11:54.898 --> 11:56.418
and maintained unity.

11:56.737 --> 11:57.977
He did it every single time.

12:02.337 --> 12:04.457
Nothing was beyond him.

12:07.697 --> 12:08.898
But I saw him just now,

12:08.898 --> 12:10.138
lying helplessly in that bed.

12:20.097 --> 12:21.298
He was so weak.

12:24.058 --> 12:25.457
The moment his heart stopped,

12:25.457 --> 12:27.138
I was absolutely terrified.

12:28.577 --> 12:29.337
I was afraid

12:30.977 --> 12:31.697
that this mountain

12:31.697 --> 12:32.778
would truly collapse.

12:32.898 --> 12:33.658
He won't.

12:34.737 --> 12:35.538
He won't.

12:37.937 --> 12:39.058
Father is strong.

12:39.217 --> 12:41.217
He'll make it, okay?

13:47.937 --> 13:49.337
Not hungry again?

13:54.178 --> 13:55.857
You're eating so little in a day.

13:57.737 --> 13:59.217
Your body can't handle this.

14:01.778 --> 14:03.457
I will worry about you.

14:16.337 --> 14:16.977
I'm sorry.

14:18.498 --> 14:19.018
Haochen.

14:22.178 --> 14:23.058
I apologize.

14:23.058 --> 14:24.298
I spoke out of turn.

14:27.298 --> 14:28.617
But no matter what,

14:31.498 --> 14:33.418
we brought you up bit by bit.

14:35.248 --> 14:36.018
When you're happy,

14:36.697 --> 14:37.778
we're happy.

14:39.617 --> 14:40.498
When you're sad,

14:41.457 --> 14:42.418
we're sad too.

14:43.138 --> 14:44.337
Haochen, you must believe.

14:45.457 --> 14:46.857
Every person in this family

14:48.617 --> 14:50.258
loves you genuinely.

14:55.498 --> 14:56.258
Haochen?

15:02.658 --> 15:03.418
Don't you

15:04.737 --> 15:06.418
like going out usually?

15:09.817 --> 15:11.298
Today, whatever you want to do,

15:11.817 --> 15:12.937
basketball,

15:13.577 --> 15:14.538
skateboarding,

15:15.337 --> 15:17.298
I'll be with you the whole time.

15:24.217 --> 15:25.697
Today, if we get tired

15:25.697 --> 15:27.058
after playing basketball,

15:27.378 --> 15:29.138
we'll have pizza.

15:29.697 --> 15:30.217
And also

15:30.217 --> 15:31.697
your favorite ice cream,

15:31.977 --> 15:32.457
okay?

15:32.817 --> 15:33.898
One scoop, two scoops.

15:33.898 --> 15:34.697
Whatever you want.

15:34.857 --> 15:35.977
After the ice-cream,

15:36.018 --> 15:37.258
we'll have pizza,

15:37.898 --> 15:38.498
steak,

15:39.280 --> 15:40.080
or fried chicken.

15:40.217 --> 15:40.898
It's up to you.

15:42.817 --> 15:43.898
Stop filming me!

15:45.937 --> 15:46.737
Put that away!

15:46.898 --> 15:47.378
Security!

15:48.138 --> 15:48.697
Security!

15:48.977 --> 15:49.817
Security, hurry!

15:49.817 --> 15:50.457
Get out!

15:50.457 --> 15:51.298
Out! Out! Out!

15:51.457 --> 15:52.298
Detain him!

15:52.778 --> 15:53.418
Get out now!

15:53.418 --> 15:53.898
You okay?

15:54.298 --> 15:55.258
It's fine. It's fine.

15:55.538 --> 15:56.058
Sweetheart.

15:56.737 --> 15:57.658
Quick. Take him away.

15:57.937 --> 15:58.817
Take him away!

15:59.778 --> 16:01.337
Stop filming! How dare you!

16:01.418 --> 16:02.378
Stop filming!

16:03.058 --> 16:04.097
Stop filming!

16:04.258 --> 16:05.217
It's okay, honey.

16:05.337 --> 16:05.977
Haochen!

16:06.258 --> 16:07.138
Handle this now!

16:07.217 --> 16:07.817
Don't worry.

16:08.097 --> 16:08.817
Haochen!

16:10.097 --> 16:11.018
Haochen!

16:11.658 --> 16:12.624
Haochen, open the door.

16:12.937 --> 16:13.617
Open up.

16:13.697 --> 16:14.352
What happened?

16:15.018 --> 16:15.977
You're finally back.

16:16.138 --> 16:16.737
I tried

16:16.737 --> 16:17.298
taking him out

16:17.298 --> 16:18.217
to cheer him up today.

16:18.217 --> 16:20.577
We got snapped right there,
not sure if it was a reporter.

16:20.577 --> 16:21.697
- Take it easy.
- He pointed it

16:21.857 --> 16:22.457
right at us,

16:22.457 --> 16:23.418
filming shamelessly.

16:23.577 --> 16:25.018
Then Haochen got upset,

16:25.018 --> 16:25.658
ran inside,

16:25.658 --> 16:27.097
and locked the door.

16:28.697 --> 16:29.258
Haochen.

16:30.577 --> 16:31.418
- Open the door!
- He...

16:31.418 --> 16:33.097
He was crying. Why is it silent now?

16:33.217 --> 16:33.778
Haochen!

16:33.778 --> 16:34.457
Haochen!

16:34.577 --> 16:35.097
Haochen!

16:37.058 --> 16:37.778
Mom, step back.

16:40.898 --> 16:41.538
Haochen.

16:42.817 --> 16:43.577
Haochen!

16:44.498 --> 16:45.298
Haochen!

16:45.737 --> 16:46.977
Haochen, what's wrong with you?

16:47.018 --> 16:47.658
Haochen!

16:47.817 --> 16:48.817
Call Dr. Wang. Hurry.

16:49.258 --> 16:49.857
Dr. Wa...

16:51.658 --> 16:52.138
Haochen.

16:53.217 --> 16:53.697
Haochen.

16:56.778 --> 16:57.418
Hello? Hello?

16:57.538 --> 16:58.058
Wang,

16:58.138 --> 16:58.817
Haochen fainted.

16:58.817 --> 16:59.697
Come to my place now.

16:59.817 --> 17:00.977
Hurry! Yes.

17:02.617 --> 17:03.378
Haochen!

17:18.377 --> 17:19.058
Dr. Wang.

17:19.538 --> 17:20.577
What's Haochen's

17:20.577 --> 17:21.897
current condition?

17:22.258 --> 17:22.897
Nothing serious.

17:23.417 --> 17:24.258
He fainted

17:24.298 --> 17:26.538
due to low blood sugar
from not eating enough.

17:27.657 --> 17:28.938
You don't know him well.

17:28.938 --> 17:30.097
He refuses to eat anything.

17:30.577 --> 17:31.577
What should we do?

17:32.698 --> 17:34.177
Due to emotional distress,

17:34.817 --> 17:35.617
now Haochen

17:35.617 --> 17:37.657
has had mild autism.

17:37.857 --> 17:39.417
That's why he refuses to eat

17:39.498 --> 17:40.298
and communicate.

17:40.458 --> 17:41.657
Mild cases can be cured.

17:41.897 --> 17:42.897
If it becomes severe,

17:43.218 --> 17:44.258
he might show signs

17:44.698 --> 17:45.258
of self-harm

17:45.298 --> 17:46.377
or aggressive behaviors.

17:46.857 --> 17:48.417
Parents should intervene early.

17:48.698 --> 17:49.698
Are there any solutions?

17:50.498 --> 17:52.657
Haochen is very resistant
to his environment right now.

17:53.218 --> 17:53.857
I think

17:54.417 --> 17:54.978
he needs

17:55.258 --> 17:56.058
a totally new

17:56.058 --> 17:56.978
environment for now.

17:58.817 --> 17:59.938
Understood. Thank you.

18:00.018 --> 18:00.417
Okay.

18:00.538 --> 18:01.577
I'll check on him again.

18:01.857 --> 18:02.817
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

18:08.738 --> 18:10.218
Haoming, Yan,

18:10.704 --> 18:12.080
let's follow the doctor's advice

18:12.377 --> 18:13.938
and take Haochen to a new environment.

18:14.337 --> 18:15.258
Anywhere will do.

18:17.258 --> 18:17.778
Mom,

18:18.978 --> 18:20.137
Dad's in the hospital now.

18:20.177 --> 18:21.298
Don't worry about Dad.

18:21.617 --> 18:22.817
His condition has stabilized.

18:22.817 --> 18:23.417
I'm here.

18:23.498 --> 18:24.377
Don't worry. I'm here.

18:24.377 --> 18:25.698
Haochen's situation is urgent.

18:27.577 --> 18:29.377
So going abroad? Somewhere far away?

18:29.417 --> 18:29.938
Good idea.

18:31.058 --> 18:32.417
But not too far.

18:33.738 --> 18:35.218
If anything happens to Dad,

18:35.888 --> 18:37.337
we might not make it back in time.

18:41.778 --> 18:43.097
So where's better?

18:47.458 --> 18:48.897
How about my grandma's house?

18:49.817 --> 18:50.377
Is that okay?

18:51.738 --> 18:52.857
Is it convenient? Because...

18:53.097 --> 18:53.738
Very convenient.

18:54.458 --> 18:55.657
She lives in the countryside.

18:55.738 --> 18:56.698
It's spacious there,

18:56.817 --> 18:57.857
with many animals.

18:58.018 --> 18:59.058
Kids love that.

19:02.817 --> 19:03.897
Let's follow Yan's advice.

19:04.738 --> 19:05.744
The hospital has nurses,

19:06.018 --> 19:06.978
and Hui's at home.

19:07.617 --> 19:09.018
Leave Dad's matters to me.

19:09.978 --> 19:11.137
Haochen's situation really

19:11.337 --> 19:12.498
can't be delayed any longer.

19:12.657 --> 19:13.258
Understood.

19:14.298 --> 19:14.857
I'll call

19:14.857 --> 19:15.778
my grandma right away.

19:15.857 --> 19:16.538
Mom, don't worry.

19:18.058 --> 19:18.864
We leave tomorrow.

19:31.817 --> 19:32.817
I told you

19:32.857 --> 19:34.177
not to wait outside.

19:34.498 --> 19:35.377
Yan!

19:35.657 --> 19:37.657
I missed you so much!

19:37.897 --> 19:38.617
Hello, Grandma.

19:39.617 --> 19:40.498
How are you lately?

19:40.498 --> 19:41.377
Good.

19:41.657 --> 19:42.857
Already in great shape,

19:42.938 --> 19:44.817
and even better seeing you all.

19:44.938 --> 19:45.577
That's great.

19:47.258 --> 19:48.978
This must be Haochen?

19:50.538 --> 19:52.137
What a handsome little fellow.

19:52.377 --> 19:54.058
Haochen, say hello to Great-grandma.

19:58.258 --> 19:58.857
Haochen.

20:01.298 --> 20:01.857
Never mind.

20:02.177 --> 20:04.298
He just arrived. He's shy.

20:04.657 --> 20:06.938
After getting familiar,
he'll call me naturally.

20:07.738 --> 20:08.417
Haochen.

20:12.738 --> 20:14.538
Come on. Give the suitcase to me.

20:14.657 --> 20:15.778
Follow me.

20:16.738 --> 20:17.538
Come on.

20:17.577 --> 20:18.577
Watch your step.

20:18.657 --> 20:20.258
Don't look around.

20:20.417 --> 20:21.897
You'll have plenty to see later.

20:22.738 --> 20:23.938
When we get home,

20:24.657 --> 20:26.538
I will cook delicious meals for you.

20:28.778 --> 20:29.177
Come on.

20:30.417 --> 20:31.417
Eat more, Haochen.

20:31.738 --> 20:33.218
I made this

20:33.577 --> 20:34.577
braised pork knuckle.

20:35.417 --> 20:37.817
- And this beef stew.
- Vinegar?

20:38.218 --> 20:39.498
I spent three to four hours

20:39.538 --> 20:41.258
simmering it.

20:41.498 --> 20:42.657
It melts in your mouth.

20:43.058 --> 20:44.498
How does the commercial say it?

20:44.897 --> 20:46.218
It tastes wonderful!

20:50.857 --> 20:52.498
You like the sliced noodles?

20:52.978 --> 20:54.498
These are special.

20:54.897 --> 20:58.018
It resembles silver fish
diving into waves

20:58.377 --> 21:00.657
and willow leaves
riding the wind from branches.

21:01.298 --> 21:02.657
If you visit Shanxi

21:02.738 --> 21:03.657
and don't eat a bowl

21:03.657 --> 21:04.897
of these noodles,

21:05.058 --> 21:06.177
it's a wasted trip.

21:08.058 --> 21:08.617
Haochen,

21:09.258 --> 21:10.018
all these dishes

21:10.538 --> 21:11.417
were prepared

21:11.498 --> 21:12.458
by Great-grandma.

21:13.018 --> 21:14.018
Come on. Eat up.

21:19.377 --> 21:20.097
Haochen?

21:22.498 --> 21:23.018
Don't.

21:26.817 --> 21:27.817
Sorry, Grandma.

21:28.177 --> 21:29.538
He's usually very polite.

21:30.258 --> 21:31.177
It's fine.

21:31.577 --> 21:32.778
He's just a child.

21:34.058 --> 21:35.258
Don't force him

21:35.258 --> 21:37.177
if he can't finish. He just arrived.

21:37.698 --> 21:39.337
Besides, Yan

21:39.897 --> 21:41.738
already told me before you came.

21:42.538 --> 21:43.978
We adults

21:44.298 --> 21:45.377
all understand

21:45.617 --> 21:46.857
children's feelings,

21:47.218 --> 21:47.817
right?

21:51.177 --> 21:52.177
Leave some for him.

21:53.104 --> 21:53.657
Leave some.

21:54.337 --> 21:55.218
No need.

21:55.617 --> 21:56.698
I'll cook fresh

21:56.778 --> 21:57.738
whenever he's hungry.

21:59.337 --> 22:00.377
You all eat now.

22:00.857 --> 22:01.738
Have some fish.

22:02.817 --> 22:03.258
Let's eat.

22:05.817 --> 22:06.377
Eat up.

22:06.377 --> 22:06.738
Okay.

22:32.538 --> 22:33.177
Yan,

22:34.177 --> 22:35.617
when I was hospitalized last time

22:35.617 --> 22:36.938
and you rushed back to see me,

22:37.938 --> 22:39.177
I realized

22:39.857 --> 22:41.577
something was wrong
between you and Haoming.

22:42.337 --> 22:43.778
But seeing you two

22:43.817 --> 22:45.018
get along so well now

22:45.938 --> 22:47.577
reassures me.

22:50.738 --> 22:51.337
So

22:51.817 --> 22:52.897
let me ask you.

22:54.137 --> 22:56.298
Was your previous conflict

22:57.258 --> 22:58.778
about him

22:59.458 --> 23:00.498
having a child?

23:09.218 --> 23:09.738
Grandma,

23:11.458 --> 23:13.377
I genuinely care for Haochen.

23:16.337 --> 23:17.538
He's such

23:17.938 --> 23:21.177
a smart, loyal and sensitive child.

23:21.897 --> 23:23.058
Before, he'd chat with me

23:23.058 --> 23:23.978
for hours.

23:25.298 --> 23:26.337
But now,

23:26.337 --> 23:27.377
he's completely silent.

23:31.938 --> 23:33.337
It hurts to see him like this.

23:35.897 --> 23:37.778
I brought him here

23:38.978 --> 23:39.897
to give him

23:39.897 --> 23:41.417
an adjustment period.

23:41.738 --> 23:42.577
He's a kid.

23:43.617 --> 23:45.298
He needs some time

23:46.218 --> 23:47.817
to process sudden life changes.

23:49.337 --> 23:50.218
I really don't know

23:50.218 --> 23:51.137
what else I should do.

23:52.258 --> 23:53.698
I just want to care for him

23:56.097 --> 23:56.978
and help him become

23:56.978 --> 23:57.897
his old self again.

23:59.978 --> 24:00.897
Yan,

24:02.857 --> 24:04.817
that's the right approach.

24:06.617 --> 24:08.417
Beyond blood relations,

24:08.458 --> 24:09.738
what matters more

24:10.337 --> 24:13.137
and truly connects people

24:13.738 --> 24:16.097
is mutual sincerity.

24:18.698 --> 24:19.258
Grandma,

24:19.698 --> 24:21.337
don't worry about us.

24:22.177 --> 24:24.617
We're being completely transparent
with each other now.

24:25.698 --> 24:28.258
We'll solve problems
and face them together.

24:30.897 --> 24:33.058
With you as our shelter,

24:33.817 --> 24:35.617
we'll overcome everything.

24:39.538 --> 24:39.978
Mom,

24:40.897 --> 24:41.698
how's Dad?

24:42.657 --> 24:44.018
He's stable in all aspects.

24:44.377 --> 24:45.538
He hasn't woken up yet.

24:46.018 --> 24:47.137
But the doctor said

24:47.377 --> 24:48.337
it is optimistic.

24:48.498 --> 24:49.617
No need to worry.

24:50.218 --> 24:50.978
That's good.

24:52.577 --> 24:53.978
Take turns with the caregivers.

24:54.384 --> 24:55.504
Don't keep staying up late.

24:56.377 --> 24:56.897
Okay.

24:57.298 --> 24:57.978
Don't worry.

24:58.978 --> 24:59.978
How's Haochen?

25:00.817 --> 25:01.617
Same as before.

25:02.177 --> 25:03.097
He still won't talk.

25:04.498 --> 25:05.577
Hopefully after some time,

25:06.377 --> 25:07.337
he'll improve.

25:07.857 --> 25:08.458
Alright.

25:09.137 --> 25:11.417
Take care over there.

25:12.218 --> 25:12.698
Okay.

25:24.738 --> 25:26.337
Haochen, breakfast is ready.

25:30.298 --> 25:30.938
Haochen?

25:33.698 --> 25:34.538
Good morning.

25:34.577 --> 25:35.177
He's out.

25:36.097 --> 25:36.698
Sleep well?

25:37.377 --> 25:38.857
Any mosquitoes last night?

25:40.458 --> 25:40.938
Come on.

25:42.817 --> 25:43.298
Look.

25:43.897 --> 25:45.417
Great-grandma made this for you.

25:45.577 --> 25:47.058
Sesame oil egg.

25:47.177 --> 25:48.177
Smell how fragrant it is.

25:50.177 --> 25:51.897
Let's have it with a steamed bun.

26:04.778 --> 26:05.978
You barely ate last night.

26:06.058 --> 26:06.817
Eat a bit more now.

26:06.817 --> 26:07.298
Haochen,

26:07.498 --> 26:08.377
it's delicious.

26:08.417 --> 26:08.938
Haochen?

26:09.657 --> 26:10.177
Haochen.

26:11.218 --> 26:12.018
Since you're done,

26:12.458 --> 26:13.177
go do some work.

26:16.458 --> 26:17.177
Haoming,

26:17.258 --> 26:18.738
you should finish your meal too.

26:18.938 --> 26:19.577
After eating,

26:19.698 --> 26:21.458
get a big basket from the yard

26:21.657 --> 26:22.417
and take the kid

26:22.832 --> 26:24.218
to harvest corn on the back hill.

26:29.698 --> 26:30.137
Okay.

26:30.617 --> 26:31.097
Understood.

26:33.498 --> 26:34.698
We country folks

26:34.698 --> 26:36.018
have one rule.

26:36.538 --> 26:38.058
Only those too old to work

26:38.337 --> 26:40.337
or infants unable to work

26:40.938 --> 26:42.058
can be exempt from labor.

26:42.177 --> 26:43.498
Everyone else can't rest.

26:43.538 --> 26:44.738
They must work the fields.

26:46.337 --> 26:47.698
You're living in my house

26:47.698 --> 26:48.577
and eating my food.

26:48.617 --> 26:50.498
Labor is mandatory.

26:50.698 --> 26:51.857
Grandma,

26:51.897 --> 26:53.097
don't be like this.

26:53.577 --> 26:55.897
Haochen is just a child.

26:56.218 --> 26:56.577
He...

26:56.817 --> 26:59.058
He can't possibly handle this work.

27:04.458 --> 27:06.337
He's quite temperamental.

27:15.258 --> 27:15.698
Brilliant.

27:17.377 --> 27:18.058
I'll go too.

27:19.137 --> 27:20.177
You haven't finished yet.

27:21.298 --> 27:22.337
Get one for him too.

27:22.458 --> 27:23.377
Get him one too.

27:23.577 --> 27:23.978
Okay.

27:38.698 --> 27:39.337
Let me show you.

27:39.698 --> 27:41.177
Corn harvesting goes like this.

27:47.698 --> 27:48.577
Press down.

27:49.617 --> 27:51.097
Twist clockwise and it comes off.

27:51.337 --> 27:52.018
Press down.

27:52.018 --> 27:53.897
Twist clockwise. Off it comes.

27:56.377 --> 27:57.657
Simple as that.

27:58.137 --> 27:59.498
Press down.

28:00.337 --> 28:01.137
Twist.

28:01.698 --> 28:02.218
Comes off.

28:08.698 --> 28:10.298
Press down and twist.

28:11.577 --> 28:12.592
The whole corn comes off.

28:15.377 --> 28:16.058
Try that one.

28:22.538 --> 28:24.857
Press down and twist.

28:46.938 --> 28:48.018
There's more over there.

28:48.417 --> 28:48.938
Go up.

28:49.657 --> 28:50.258
Up higher.

28:52.458 --> 28:53.298
No, no, no.

28:54.458 --> 28:55.738
Catch it. Catch it.

28:55.897 --> 28:56.337
Catch!

28:56.417 --> 28:57.258
Use hands!

28:57.498 --> 28:58.458
Use your hands to catch.

28:58.938 --> 28:59.778
Come out of the coop!

29:04.738 --> 29:05.137
Catch!

29:07.538 --> 29:08.498
Catch it! Catch it!

29:09.258 --> 29:10.218
Got it! I got it!

29:10.458 --> 29:11.337
Haochen, take it!

29:11.377 --> 29:11.857
Quick!

29:11.897 --> 29:13.738
Hurry! Hurry!

29:31.538 --> 29:32.817
You're dragging your feet

29:32.857 --> 29:34.218
on such a small task.

29:34.417 --> 29:34.938
Do you plan

29:34.938 --> 29:36.298
to finish it when it's dark?

29:37.538 --> 29:38.617
Why are you staring?

29:39.577 --> 29:40.298
Let me tell you.

29:40.377 --> 29:41.498
All these corns

29:41.538 --> 29:43.258
must be processed before sunset.

29:56.688 --> 29:57.328
How about this?

29:58.538 --> 29:59.577
You handle that pile.

30:00.097 --> 30:01.018
These two are mine.

30:16.897 --> 30:17.377
Okay.

30:17.577 --> 30:18.698
Here, take it.

30:56.657 --> 30:57.298
Haochen,

30:57.778 --> 30:59.617
do you want another bowl?

31:03.458 --> 31:04.377
Go to the kitchen

31:04.624 --> 31:05.458
and serve yourself.

31:17.738 --> 31:18.577
Farm work

31:18.978 --> 31:19.738
really works.

31:20.978 --> 31:21.938
Second serve already.

31:23.778 --> 31:24.738
Remember to tell Mom

31:25.298 --> 31:26.337
about the good news.

31:26.538 --> 31:27.058
Definitely.

31:28.058 --> 31:29.337
Won't this cause indigestion?

31:40.258 --> 31:41.097
Let me help you.

31:41.177 --> 31:41.657
Let me help.

31:47.657 --> 31:48.058
Come on.

31:52.337 --> 31:53.738
Meat lover should eat more.

31:56.458 --> 31:57.857
Eat more meat.

31:58.097 --> 31:58.897
This kid...

32:01.218 --> 32:01.776
His belly...

32:09.097 --> 32:10.298
Though we've now

32:10.698 --> 32:11.738
removed Shen Jinsong

32:11.738 --> 32:13.258
and Shen Haoming from their positions,

32:15.218 --> 32:16.817
they remain the company's

32:16.938 --> 32:17.698
major shareholders.

32:18.058 --> 32:20.258
The board and department heads

32:20.897 --> 32:22.377
are all waiting to see

32:24.177 --> 32:25.498
when they'll make a comeback.

32:28.657 --> 32:29.617
What's your take?

32:35.177 --> 32:37.177
Due to their personal misconduct,

32:37.377 --> 32:38.857
our stock prices plummeted,

32:39.097 --> 32:40.538
causing massive financial losses.

32:42.657 --> 32:43.538
Legally speaking,

32:44.258 --> 32:45.498
the group has full authority

32:45.978 --> 32:47.337
to demand compensation from them.

32:47.978 --> 32:49.137
We can gather

32:50.137 --> 32:51.377
eligible shareholders

32:52.432 --> 32:53.808
to represent the group

32:53.808 --> 32:56.177
in suing those two

32:56.657 --> 32:57.978
and demand they repay the losses.

32:59.137 --> 33:01.298
Meanwhile, file
for litigation preservation

33:01.657 --> 33:02.817
to freeze their accounts.

33:03.417 --> 33:04.498
A legal battle?

33:06.458 --> 33:07.817
It has lengthy cycles.

33:08.258 --> 33:09.817
The longer, the better.

33:10.617 --> 33:11.738
Once preservation is enacted

33:12.097 --> 33:13.258
and their accounts frozen,

33:13.857 --> 33:14.857
all their stocks

33:15.337 --> 33:16.617
become worthless paper.

33:17.337 --> 33:18.137
Without funds,

33:18.498 --> 33:19.698
how could they come back?

33:34.058 --> 33:34.538
Senior,

33:34.698 --> 33:36.738
the patient in Bed 3
has surgery scheduled Friday.

33:38.978 --> 33:39.498
Lin?

33:42.698 --> 33:43.498
You're back.

33:46.337 --> 33:47.498
Are you going out?

33:47.657 --> 33:48.097
Yeah,

33:48.137 --> 33:50.137
I need to return to the office.

33:52.657 --> 33:54.097
Have you been avoiding me lately?

33:54.617 --> 33:56.137
Why would I do that? I'm not.

34:01.097 --> 34:01.577
Lin.

34:04.018 --> 34:05.058
I know you're busy lately,

34:06.417 --> 34:07.897
but you only text two-word replies.

34:08.378 --> 34:09.617
Calls last less than a minute.

34:10.257 --> 34:11.858
When I offer
to pick you up, you decline.

34:13.808 --> 34:14.818
What's really going on?

34:16.418 --> 34:17.697
You're overthinking.

34:18.418 --> 34:19.898
I've just

34:19.978 --> 34:21.058
been too busy lately.

34:21.257 --> 34:22.617
I'm too occupied.

34:24.177 --> 34:24.978
Look,

34:25.257 --> 34:26.657
I finally left work early today,

34:26.657 --> 34:28.058
hoping to rest,

34:28.080 --> 34:29.552
but they called and dragged me back.

34:30.297 --> 34:31.217
It's genuinely chaotic.

34:31.938 --> 34:33.018
I have much to do.

34:33.018 --> 34:33.978
You go rest first.

34:34.177 --> 34:35.418
I'll update you later.

34:35.697 --> 34:36.137
Go back.

34:36.137 --> 34:36.617
Really?

34:36.657 --> 34:37.338
Really.

34:41.418 --> 34:42.257
It's not too bad.

34:42.538 --> 34:43.498
Just a minor sprain.

34:44.858 --> 34:46.458
Apply cold compress when you go back.

34:46.657 --> 34:47.938
Then use the medicinal oil

34:47.978 --> 34:48.898
and massage the ankle.

34:48.898 --> 34:50.032
It'll be fine in a few days.

34:50.378 --> 34:51.217
Thank you, doctor.

34:53.097 --> 34:54.538
The swelling looks significant.

34:56.938 --> 34:57.538
It's my fault.

34:57.777 --> 34:58.777
I didn't catch you.

34:59.018 --> 34:59.577
No, no.

34:59.697 --> 35:00.818
I just lost my balance.

35:03.257 --> 35:04.018
Maybe you should

35:04.018 --> 35:04.818
take some days off

35:05.392 --> 35:06.217
and work from home.

35:06.978 --> 35:07.538
No need.

35:07.538 --> 35:08.898
It's not a serious injury.

35:09.018 --> 35:10.498
With so many things in the company,

35:10.538 --> 35:11.538
I still need to go.

35:12.137 --> 35:12.617
Lin,

35:13.177 --> 35:13.938
are you okay?

35:14.297 --> 35:15.018
I looked for you

35:15.378 --> 35:16.418
and heard from security.

35:16.978 --> 35:17.617
How did you

35:17.617 --> 35:18.577
end up falling?

35:19.018 --> 35:19.978
It must hurt terribly.

35:20.177 --> 35:20.938
Let me see.

35:22.097 --> 35:22.858
I'm fine. Really.

35:22.858 --> 35:23.538
What you doing?

35:26.177 --> 35:27.177
You're injured.

35:27.177 --> 35:28.657
Why are you carrying this yourself?

35:28.858 --> 35:29.538
Dr. Yu,

35:29.818 --> 35:30.577
thank you.

35:30.858 --> 35:31.818
Leave the rest to me.

35:32.272 --> 35:33.297
Are you out of your mind?

35:34.058 --> 35:35.257
What's wrong with you?

35:35.617 --> 35:36.577
This is my girlfriend.

35:39.418 --> 35:39.938
Lin,

35:41.458 --> 35:42.577
you didn't tell him?

35:45.297 --> 35:46.058
Tell me what?

35:46.858 --> 35:48.458
Qiao Lin is now my girlfriend.

35:48.752 --> 35:49.538
Don't believe me?

35:50.978 --> 35:51.938
Ask her yourself then.

36:04.898 --> 36:05.418
Lin,

36:05.737 --> 36:06.378
let me help you.

36:09.818 --> 36:10.818
Thank you, doctor.

36:11.898 --> 36:12.297
Lin,

36:12.400 --> 36:13.418
let's go. I'll help you.

36:13.697 --> 36:14.217
No need.

36:14.818 --> 36:15.297
Lin,

36:15.657 --> 36:16.378
tell me the truth.

36:17.338 --> 36:17.978
Back off.

36:18.378 --> 36:18.938
Yu Yiming,

36:19.217 --> 36:20.217
this is your workplace.

36:20.617 --> 36:22.217
You'll regret it if you start a fight.

36:26.097 --> 36:26.617
Lin,

36:28.137 --> 36:29.217
are you hiding something?

36:32.978 --> 36:34.297
What kind of nonsense is that?

36:34.737 --> 36:36.577
We're in a proper relationship.

36:36.938 --> 36:38.058
We're deeply connected.

36:38.458 --> 36:39.898
True lovers always find their way.

36:40.378 --> 36:41.538
What do we need to hide?

36:41.737 --> 36:42.498
Get out of my way.

36:44.338 --> 36:45.617
I need to talk to Qiao Lin now.

36:48.617 --> 36:49.177
Lin,

36:50.177 --> 36:52.097
make it clear to him once and for all.

36:52.938 --> 36:54.137
Make him give up completely.

36:59.697 --> 37:00.498
Lin Tao and I

37:02.418 --> 37:03.498
are back together.

37:16.137 --> 37:16.858
That's impossible.

37:19.978 --> 37:20.657
Yu Yiming,

37:22.217 --> 37:23.577
the time I spent with you

37:23.577 --> 37:24.737
was truly joyful.

37:27.257 --> 37:28.498
But marriage and dating

37:28.498 --> 37:29.538
are two different things.

37:32.137 --> 37:33.498
I've thought long and hard.

37:34.818 --> 37:36.217
There are significant gaps

37:36.257 --> 37:37.338
between us.

37:38.577 --> 37:39.777
These are practical realities.

37:43.657 --> 37:44.577
As for Lin Tao,

37:45.538 --> 37:46.257
his devotion

37:46.257 --> 37:47.458
has truly moved me.

37:47.697 --> 37:49.498
After much consideration,

37:50.498 --> 37:51.097
I believe

37:52.378 --> 37:53.458
he's more suitable for me.

37:59.378 --> 38:00.018
I don't believe

38:00.018 --> 38:01.018
anything you just said.

38:02.177 --> 38:03.338
What really happened?

38:04.577 --> 38:05.577
If he threatened you...

38:05.617 --> 38:06.297
Yu Yiming,

38:06.657 --> 38:07.777
if you touch my girl again,

38:07.818 --> 38:09.018
I'll hit you. I swear.

38:09.097 --> 38:10.458
Lin Tao, that's enough!

38:19.617 --> 38:20.297
Yu Yiming,

38:20.697 --> 38:21.498
believe it or not,

38:21.498 --> 38:22.858
I've said everything that needed

38:22.858 --> 38:23.818
to be said today.

38:25.378 --> 38:26.418
Don't come to me anymore.

38:27.058 --> 38:27.617
Lin,

38:28.737 --> 38:30.297
now that everything's out in the open,

38:31.458 --> 38:32.697
return what you owe him.

38:33.458 --> 38:34.978
So he won't bother you again.

38:41.818 --> 38:43.137
This ring was also given by you.

38:47.137 --> 38:47.777
Take it back.

38:50.777 --> 38:51.697
Now we're even.

39:20.617 --> 39:21.657
Haochen,

39:23.058 --> 39:24.097
what are you looking at?

39:26.898 --> 39:28.538
You like animals too?

39:29.338 --> 39:30.338
Great.

39:30.777 --> 39:32.217
From now on, these chicks

39:32.498 --> 39:33.697
will be your responsibility.

39:34.338 --> 39:35.538
Actually, taking care of them

39:35.538 --> 39:36.617
is pretty simple.

39:36.818 --> 39:37.858
You just need

39:38.257 --> 39:39.297
to feed them

39:39.378 --> 39:40.697
regularly every day.

39:42.058 --> 39:43.458
That's about it.

39:44.418 --> 39:45.338
And also

39:46.338 --> 39:47.657
clean their living area

39:47.737 --> 39:48.978
thoroughly every day.

39:49.058 --> 39:49.737
Keep it tidy.

39:50.338 --> 39:50.737
Okay?

39:51.458 --> 39:52.378
Simple enough, right?

39:52.657 --> 39:53.257
Here.

39:53.737 --> 39:54.657
Take this.

39:55.338 --> 39:56.137
Three meals a day

39:56.177 --> 39:57.217
are your job now.

39:57.257 --> 39:58.257
If they get hungry,

39:58.297 --> 39:59.418
I'll hold you accountable.

40:00.697 --> 40:01.217
Get to work.

40:38.202 --> 40:40.432
(Xu Yan)

40:52.458 --> 40:53.097
Yan.

40:53.737 --> 40:55.137
I saw the payment went through.

40:55.657 --> 40:56.097
Yes.

40:56.538 --> 40:58.137
The loan funds have arrived.

40:58.697 --> 40:59.137
Also

40:59.297 --> 41:01.297
the physical store is progressing.

41:01.297 --> 41:02.577
Though it might

41:02.617 --> 41:03.818
not move as quickly.

41:05.697 --> 41:06.297
Don't worry.

41:06.938 --> 41:08.818
I'll take care of both
the company and home.

41:09.217 --> 41:09.657
Okay.

41:09.904 --> 41:10.898
Then I'll count on you.

41:12.338 --> 41:12.898
Thank you.

41:13.072 --> 41:13.818
You too.

41:14.297 --> 41:14.737
Bye.

41:15.217 --> 41:15.737
Bye.

41:41.257 --> 41:42.018
Be careful

41:42.018 --> 41:42.978
with this mirror too.

41:43.018 --> 41:43.418
Lin.

41:43.458 --> 41:43.898
Thank you.

41:46.458 --> 41:46.858
Lin.

41:54.097 --> 41:54.777
What is it?

41:57.018 --> 41:58.018
Are you moving out?

42:00.097 --> 42:00.898
Where to?

42:01.617 --> 42:02.657
T-To my sister's place.

42:05.538 --> 42:06.538
No matter how I ask,

42:06.704 --> 42:07.978
you refuse to tell the truth.

42:07.978 --> 42:08.418
Is that so?

42:09.177 --> 42:10.297
There's no truth to tell.

42:10.297 --> 42:10.737
Just...

42:11.458 --> 42:13.177
I told you. I've just
had a change of heart.

42:15.538 --> 42:17.297
I don't care how many times
you've said it

42:18.338 --> 42:19.297
or what I've seen

42:19.297 --> 42:19.898
or heard.

42:20.097 --> 42:22.338
Even if you are with Lin Tao
and push me away,

42:23.378 --> 42:25.058
I'll never believe
you've changed feelings.

42:32.297 --> 42:33.217
If you'd seen

42:34.418 --> 42:35.577
how you looked at me,

42:37.137 --> 42:38.737
you'd understand
why I'm certain of this.

42:41.257 --> 42:41.777
Miss Qiao,

42:41.978 --> 42:42.898
things are packed.

42:43.657 --> 42:44.097
Let's go.

42:44.217 --> 42:44.617
Okay.

42:48.097 --> 42:48.818
We're adults.

42:48.858 --> 42:49.577
Act more mature.

43:19.378 --> 43:20.058
Can you do it?

43:22.058 --> 43:22.737
Yan.

43:23.777 --> 43:24.378
Yan.

43:28.257 --> 43:29.338
We know

43:29.378 --> 43:30.538
you're staying at Grandma's.

43:30.538 --> 43:31.617
So we came to check.

43:34.818 --> 43:36.538
Well, where is Haoming

43:37.177 --> 43:37.697
and Haochen?

43:38.177 --> 43:40.177
Haoming took Haochen to do farm work.

43:40.378 --> 43:41.097
Farm work?

43:41.538 --> 43:42.858
Can Haoming and Haochen

43:43.137 --> 43:44.338
handle farm work?

43:44.858 --> 43:46.297
They're guests from afar.

43:46.338 --> 43:47.858
We can't make guests work, right?

43:47.938 --> 43:48.938
I'll talk to Mom.

43:48.938 --> 43:50.378
Grandma's made great arrangements.

43:51.657 --> 43:52.818
They're eating well

43:52.898 --> 43:53.737
and sleeping well.

43:54.538 --> 43:55.938
So you don't need to worry.

43:58.137 --> 44:00.177
Also, I brought Haochen here

44:00.177 --> 44:01.177
to leave him

44:03.978 --> 44:04.978
some peace and quiet.

44:06.018 --> 44:06.898
If you want

44:06.898 --> 44:07.978
to see him,

44:08.858 --> 44:10.097
maybe you should come later

44:10.498 --> 44:11.818
when he's in better condition.

44:11.898 --> 44:12.378
Okay?

44:16.137 --> 44:16.458
Okay.

44:16.498 --> 44:18.217
S-Since that's the case,

44:18.217 --> 44:19.097
then we won't

44:21.137 --> 44:22.697
bother you anymore.

44:22.777 --> 44:23.137
I...

44:24.498 --> 44:26.217
Th-These are for your grandma.

44:26.257 --> 44:28.378
These are her calcium tablets

44:28.378 --> 44:29.058
and fish oil.

44:29.538 --> 44:30.858
These are snacks

44:30.858 --> 44:32.177
for Haochen.

44:32.257 --> 44:33.617
Kids love these.

44:35.697 --> 44:36.418
And this...

44:42.858 --> 44:44.177
This is the money

44:44.938 --> 44:46.097
you gave me for treatment.

44:46.097 --> 44:46.818
I didn't use it.

44:47.338 --> 44:49.058
The doctor said the tumor was benign.

44:49.058 --> 44:51.088
After the minimally invasive surgery,
I'm fine now.

44:52.217 --> 44:54.498
We heard what happened
to the Shen family.

44:56.858 --> 44:58.458
Now that you've moved back here,

44:59.458 --> 45:02.097
it's convenient for us
to visit from the town.

45:03.120 --> 45:04.938
If you need anything,
be sure to call us.

45:07.257 --> 45:09.058
We can't help much in Jingzhou,

45:09.418 --> 45:10.338
but in our hometown,

45:10.938 --> 45:12.657
we'll definitely find ways to assist,

45:13.058 --> 45:13.538
right?

45:14.257 --> 45:15.257
Take this money.

45:15.898 --> 45:16.858
If it's not enough,

45:17.737 --> 45:18.858
just call us.

45:19.177 --> 45:20.257
We still have savings.

45:33.257 --> 45:33.898
Thank you.

45:39.898 --> 45:41.297
We're family. No need for thanks.

45:42.777 --> 45:43.498
We're leaving now.

46:13.418 --> 46:14.097
You rest first.

46:14.458 --> 46:15.344
I'll get your clothes.

46:16.097 --> 46:17.378
When water's hot, take a bath.

46:21.018 --> 46:22.137
It's cold. Drink slowly.

